  "title": "Delivery Driver",
  "description": "<p></p><p><strong>Working Days: 5 Days week</strong><br /><strong>Location : West.</strong><br /><strong>Vehicle : Company Van provided</strong></p><p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Load, transport, and deliver items safely and within designated timeframes.</li><li>Conduct pickups and deliveries for assigned areas as per company requirements</li><li>Prioritize and ensure timely delivery of urgent or high-priority goods</li><li>Verify orders before and after delivery to confirm accuracy and customer satisfaction.</li><li>Maintain the vehicle in proper working condition and report any issues promptly.</li><li>Follow assigned routes and adhere to scheduled delivery times.</li><li>Any other ad-hoc duties as assigned by the supervisors</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Possesses <strong>Class 3 Driving License</strong></li><li>At Least 1 year of driving experience</li><li>Able to handle loading/unloading of goods</li></ul>",
